# Internal planning / working docs (not part of the public package).
# Root-anchored on purpose: unanchored names match at ANY depth and once
# swallowed docs/runbooks/audit-coherence.md on case-insensitive systems.
/docs/superpowers/
/CLAUDE.md
/AGENTS.md
/GEMINI.md
/AUDIT.md
/AUDIT-COHERENCE.md
