/coherence-report.md
/coherence-report.json
/docs/coherence-snapshots/*.png
!/docs/coherence-snapshots/.gitkeep
# SSOT docs-build outputs that stay regenerable (npm run docs:build).
# Only the artifacts actually consumed by the web app are committed:
# apps/web/src/app/docs/sections/*.section.tsx (wired into /docs).
# Everything below is emitted by the pipeline but not imported anywhere yet.
README.generated.md
CHANGELOG.generated.md
/scripts/build-docs/bundle-sizes.json
/packages/ui-kit/src/registry.generated.ts
/apps/web/src/app/ui-kit/sections/
/apps/web/src/app/ui-kit/*/metadata.generated.ts
# OG images: real PNGs rendered via Playwright (orchestrator step or the
# standalone generate-og-images CLI). Generated artifacts — regenerate with
# `npm run docs:build`; kept out of git.
/apps/web/public/og/
